		title: Release the Prisoners!
		unique: false
		side: Shadow
		culture: Sauron
		twilight: 2
		type: Condition
		target: self
		keywords: Support Area
		effects: [
			{
				type: Activated
				phase: Maneuver
				cost: [
					{
						type: Exert
						select: choose(Sauron, minion)
					}
					{
						type: RemoveCardsInDeadPileFromGame
						select: choose(companion)
						memorize: flungComp
					}
				]
				effect: [
					{
						type: Exert
						select: all(CultureFromMemory(flungComp), character)
					}
					{
						type: Hinder
						select: self
					}
				]
			}
		]
		gametext: Maneuver: Exert a [sauron] minion and remove a companion in the dead pile from the game to exert every character sharing a culture with that companion.  Hinder this condition.
		lore: "It tumbled down, small round shot that did not burn. But when men ran to learn what it might be, they cried aloud or wept."
